<title>mạ ạ̉sʿd ạlbyt ạldẖy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mạ ạ̉sʿd ạlbyt ạldẖy qd ḥl fyh ạbn ạlʿly
 ḥytẖ ạlmsyḥ ạlmftdy (ạ̉ḍḥy̱ rỷys ạlmnzl)2
 ạlqrạr - ṭwby̱ lbyt qạỷm ạ̉sạsh ạldyn ạlṣḥyḥ
 ṭwby̱ lbyt fạḍl (sẖʿạrh ḥb ạlmsyḥ)2
 2- fy dẖlk ạlbyt ạlsʿyd yswd br wwỷạm
 ạ̹dẖ rwḥ fạdynạ ạlmjyd (qd ḥl fyh wạlslạm)2
 3- lạ bgẖḍ fyh lạ ḥsd lạ sẖyʾ ydʿw llkẖṣạm
 fy ḥrzh ynfy ạlkmd (fy ryʿh yḥlw ạlnẓạm)2</lyrics>
</song>